  "text": "The electrostatic interactions between ligand and receptor binding pocket play a crucial role in agonist or inverse agonist action [CITATION_1] ). Our results suggest that the chlorine atoms are crucial to the potentiating effect of p,p´-DDT on FSHR. This is further illustrated by the inhibiting effect of the 10 -5 M BPA, which is chlorine-free.",
